{"type": "article", "id": 7912, "title": "微软如何宣传手环：让 WWE 的摔跤选手代言", "description": "苹果请超模，微软请肌肉男。", "date": "2015-03-30T13:00:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8358, "name": "摔跤"}, {"id": 8359, "name": "WrestleMania"}, {"id": 1792, "name": "手环"}, {"id": 260, "name": "微软"}, {"id": 8360, "name": "WWE"}, {"id": 8361, "name": "Ryback"}, {"id": 8362, "name": "Dolph Ziggler"}], "category": 4, "column": null, "author": 1375, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125626raEy083nhHdTJYDj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:22px;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;cursor:text !important;\">\r\n\t北京时间早上 7 点，第 31 届摔跤狂热大赛（WrestleMania）在加州的李维斯体育馆打响。这场摔跤比赛是美国职业摔跤 WWE 的旗舰赛事，被誉为<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E5%B1%8A%E6%91%94%E8%A7%92%E7%8B%82%E7%83%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%B5%9B\" target=\"_blank\">体育娱乐界的超级碗</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:22px;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;cursor:text !important;\">\r\n\t而在比赛前的准备阶段，<a href=\"http://www.neowin.net/news/microsoft-teams-up-with-the-wwe-to-promote-the-band-ahead-of-wrestlemania\" target=\"_blank\">微软找来了 WWE 旗下的两位摔角选手</a> Ryback 和 Dolph Ziggler，推广<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/3199.html\" target=\"_blank\">去年推出的手环 Microsoft Band</a>。当他们在为比赛训练时，微软会将他们跑步、健身和睡觉等监测数据<a href=\"http://www.wwe.com/inside/microsoft-bands-track-superstars\" target=\"_blank\">同步至官网</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:22px;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;cursor:text !important;\">\r\n\t当然，如果能在摔跤比赛中看到实时监测数据，应该会是更有趣的体验。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:22px;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;cursor:text !important;\">\r\n\t微软选择的两位 WWE 选手，并不仅仅是针对摔跤比赛这点。Ryback 在前几个月回归后，努力摆脱前一个角色的定位，“<a href=\"http://www.givemesport.com/517063-wwe-ryback-wants-to-be-fans-hero-after-comeback-regrets-previous-role\" style=\"cursor:pointer !important;\">希望成为粉丝心中的英雄</a>”。而另一位 Dolph Ziggler 则被滚石誉为 <a href=\"http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/features/wwe-wrestler-of-the-year-dolph-ziggler-20141217\" target=\"_blank\">2014 年年度摔角手</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:22px;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;cursor:text !important;\">\r\n\t对于现在的微软来说，这样的形象符合市场营销的定位。毕竟新版 Windows 系统可能是微软目前重回一流科技公司的最大的可能性。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:22px;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;cursor:text !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:22px;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;cursor:text !important;\">\r\n\t题图来自：<a href=\"http://my.fakingnews.firstpost.com/2014/04/30/supreme-court-orders-management-change-at-wwe-after-match-fixing-reports/\">fakingnews</a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}